Revision history for Net-Async-Statsd

0.004     2016-12-27 20:34:39+08:00 Asia/Kuala_Lumpur
	New features:
	* Server protocol accepts (and ignores) extra information on a line, such as
	tags or comments

0.004     2014-08-29 06:16:01+01:00 Europe/London
	New features:
	* Support for prefix option in client

0.003     2014-08-27 03:50:57+01:00 Europe/London
	No new features

	Bugs fixed:
	* Retain the queue_stat Future to avoid ->then in void context,
	as a precaution for when UDP ->send gains the ability to resolve the
	future on completion

	Dependency fixes:
	* sum0 is a relatively new addition to List::Util

0.002     2014-08-09 18:25:21+01:00 Europe/London
	No new features

	Dependency fixes:
	* Added IO::Socket::IP to cpanfile

0.001     2014-08-04 15:44:06+01:00 Europe/London
	Initial CPAN release
